quiet( library(dplyr) )
quiet( library(ggplot2) )
quiet( require(gridExtra) )

train$label <- as.factor(label_train$V1)
test$label <- as.factor(label_test$V1)
train$subjectID <- as.factor(subjectID_train$V1)
test$subjectID <- as.factor(subjectID_test$V1)
train$partition <- as.factor("train")
test$partition <- as.factor("test")
train <- train %>% mutate(czynnosc = as.factor(ifelse(label == 1, "WALKING", 
                                               ifelse(label == 2, "WALKING_UPSTAIRS", 
                                                      ifelse(label == 3, "WALKING_DOWNSTAIRS",
                                                             ifelse(label == 4, "SITTING",
                                                                    ifelse(label == 5, "STANDING", "LAYING")))))))
test <- test %>% mutate(czynnosc = as.factor(ifelse(label == 1, "WALKING", 
                                          ifelse(label == 2, "WALKING_UPSTAIRS", 
                                                 ifelse(label == 3, "WALKING_DOWNSTAIRS",
                                                        ifelse(label == 4, "SITTING",
                                                               ifelse(label == 5, "STANDING", "LAYING")))))))
full_data <- rbind(train, test)

Liczba eksperymentów każdego rodzaju

qplot(data = full_data, x = subjectID, fill = czynnosc) +
  geom_vline(xintercept=21.5, linetype="dashed", color = "black")

Srednie prędkość w każdym z kierunków

tmp <- full_data %>% filter(subjectID == 1) %>% arrange(label) %>% mutate(index = row_number())

tmp %>%
  ggplot(aes(x=index, y = X1, colour = czynnosc, alpha = 0.4)) +
  geom_point() + ylab("średnia przyspieszomierz X") + xlab("")

tmp %>%
  ggplot(aes(x=index, y = X2, colour = czynnosc, alpha = 0.4)) +
  geom_point() + ylab("średnia przyspieszomierz Y") + xlab("")

tmp %>%
  ggplot(aes(x=index, y = X3, colour = czynnosc, alpha = 0.4)) +
  geom_point() + ylab("średnia przyspieszomierz Z") + xlab("")

Prędkości po duskretnej transformacie Fouriera

train %>% ggplot(aes(x = X275, y = X276, colour = czynnosc)) + geom_point() + ggtitle("train") +
              xlab("maximum przyspieszeniomierza X po FFT") + ylab("maximum przyspieszeniomierza Y po FFT")

test %>% ggplot(aes(x = X275, y = X276, colour = czynnosc)) + geom_point() + ggtitle("test") +
              xlab("maximum przyspieszeniomierza X po FFT") + ylab("maximum przyspieszeniomierza Y po FFT")

PCA

tmp <- train[,1:561]
data_pca <- prcomp(tmp, scale. = TRUE, center = TRUE)

tmp <- as.data.frame(cbind(data_pca$x[,1:100], train$czynnosc))
tmp$czynnosc <- as.factor(tmp$V101)
tmp %>% ggplot(aes(x = PC1, y=PC2, color = czynnosc)) + geom_point()

tmp %>% ggplot(aes(x = PC1, y=PC4, color = czynnosc)) + geom_point()
